columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the domain.

columns.name: creation_time
columns.description: A timestamp that indicates when the domain was created.

columns.name: app_network_access_type
columns.description: Specifies the VPC used for non-EFS traffic.

columns.name: app_security_group_management
columns.description: The entity that creates and manages the required security groups for inter-app communication in VPCOnly mode.

columns.name: home_efs_file_system_id
columns.description: The ID of the Amazon Elastic File System (EFS) managed by this domain.

columns.name: kms_key_id
columns.description: The Amazon Web Services KMS customer managed key used to encrypt the EFS volume attached to the domain.

columns.name: security_group_id_for_domain_boundary
columns.description: The ID of the security group that authorizes traffic between the RSessionGateway apps and the RStudioServerPro app.

columns.name: single_sign_on_managed_application_instance_id
columns.description: The SSO managed application instance ID.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: The list of tags for the domain.

columns.name: default_user_settings
columns.description: Settings which are applied to UserProfiles in this domain if settings are not explicitly specified in a given UserProfile.

columns.name: subnet_ids
columns.description: The VPC subnets that studio uses for communication.
